Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,原来妈妈是个大小姐啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈?妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回 我们的仙境 重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么大小姐嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是!
